description:
"You're a big boy for an 18 year old!"
Our camera guys were understandably fascinated with Dan's big muscles. At 215 pounds, he's definitely packing!
"I spend a lot of time in the gym," he said. "It's exciting to see myself grow."
He's fresh out of high school.
"I just graduated this June," he said.
He was a jock in high school, being on the football, basketball, baseball, and hockey teams.
He's started community college and plans on going to a four-year university from there.
"I want to study business and finance," he said. "Everyone in my family are accountants."
title: Dan
